<div class='row'>
<div class="span3">
  <%= render 'shared/static_nav' %>
</div><!-- //span3 -->
<div class="span9">
  <div class='about-lnc'>
    <div class='about-header'>
      <h2>About Friendskis</h2>
    </div>
    <div class='what'>
      <h3>What is Friendskis?</h3>
      <p>
      Friendskis is an app that helps you discover and connect with new people on Facebook. Our aim is to help you broaden your circle of friends in a safe and anonymous environment whilst also having some fun! 
      </p>
      <p>
      Friendskis works by allowing you to share photos from your Facebook profile anonymously. If you think someone’s photo is cool, vote up their photo or even better, send them a message. 
      </p>
      <p>
      We keep everything on Friendskis anonymous until you decide to share your Facebook identity with whoever you are talking to. Simple as that! 
      </p>
    </div><!-- //what -->
    <div class='who'>
      <h3>Who is Friendskis?</h3>
      <div class='founder-info'>
        <h5>Ralph Wintle <span>Founder</span></h5>
        <p>
        Hello there! My name is Ralph and I founded Friendskis in the Summer of 2012. I built Friendskis because I felt that online dating sites today suck!
        </p>
        <p>
        I realized that I would much rather check out someone’s Facebook profile before meeting them to make sure they were normal - plus I really enjoyed checking out other people’s photos! 
        </p>
        <p>
        I sincerely hope you enjoy using Friendskis and that it helps solve a similar problem for you. 
        </p>
      </div><!-- //founder-info -->
      <div class='founder-profile'>
        <%= image_tag 'profile_beach.jpg', style: 'width: 110px' %>
      </div><!-- //founder-profile -->
    </div><!-- //who -->
    <div class='contact'>
      <h3>Leave your Feedback!</h3>
      <p>
        I would love to hear your feedback in the comments section below or on our <%= link_to "Facebook app page", "https://www.facebook.com/friendskis" %>. 
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="fb-comments" data-href="https://friendskis.com/about" data-num-posts="6" data-width="540"></div>
  </div><!-- //about-lnc -->
</div><!-- //span9 -->
</div>




